          "text": "retrieve downed waterfowl. The\nmodern Golden Retriever belongs to the Sporting Group in\nthe American Kennel Club, and was recognized as an official\nbreed by that organization in 1925. \nBreed Characteristics\nPresent day Golden Retrievers are a medium sized dog that\ngenerally mature to around 65lbs. They are distinguished by\ntheir classic golden yellow double coat of medium to long\nhair. Routine grooming is a necessity to help maintain their\nlustrous coat, and minimize shedding. Their solid build ",
