          "text": ", any\nsign of aggression (apart from a female with very young\npuppies) should be cause for concern. Responsible breeders\nshould be invested in finding the best homes possible for\ntheir puppies, so expect lots of questions and detailed\nconversations about setting new puppies up for success. Seek\nout breeders who are willing and able to provide support and\ninformation long after you take your new addition home.\nMost breed enthusiasts will be involved in confirmation\nexhibitions or other sports to ",
