          "text": "ll apply. Look for a\nhappy, outgoing dog who is willing to approach and engage\nwith you. Given that the shelter environment can be\noverwhelming for some dogs, some level of initial reticence or\nshyness may be seen. Taking dogs for a brief walk outside of\nthe rescue can sometimes help them relax and bring out more\nof their true personality.   \nRegardless of their origins, having a member of the Golden\nRetriever breed as a household member can be a true\ndelight. With appropriate training, most Gol",
