        {
          "text": "den\nRetriever breed as a household member can be a true\ndelight. With appropriate training, most Goldens are willing\nand able to participate in a variety of adventures and\nexperiences. The cheerfulness of the Golden is nearly\nimpossible to resist and their unbridled joy in the simple\npleasures of life is truly infectious! They are dogs that are\nalways ready for the next adventure or for a quiet snuggle on\nthe couch!\nWWW.BEYONDTHEDOGTRAINING.COM/KANSAS-CITY/DOG-TRAINING/\n",
