      "Meet-the-Pug.pdf": [
        {
          "text": "Meet the Pug\nThe Big Little Dog!\nMost people are attracted to Pugs because of their small size, sweet nature, curly tail and pushed-in face. Pugs can \nhave appeal for every age, sex and type of human! They are small but sturdy; rough and tumble yet sensitive and \nsincere. There is nothing a Pug will not try. Their diminutive size is no deterrent if they are approached by an \naggressive large dog. Pugs are undaunted in a fight, though it is not typical of them to start a skirmish unless \njealousy",
