        {
          "text": "next to the baby\u2019s body. Pugs are equally happy watching the daytime \n\u2018soaps\u2019 on your lap, or going for a romp in the woods, as long as they are with you. Older Pugs that have slowed \ndown a bit are the best pet for the aged that you could ever find.\nThe Pug can fill different needs for different people. Regardless of your lifestyle, a Pug will overwhelm you with \ncompanionship. This is what they were always intended to do.\nPurpose and Origin\nThe Pug\u2019s primary purpose has always been exclusively",
