        {
          "text": "were always intended to do.\nPurpose and Origin\nThe Pug\u2019s primary purpose has always been exclusively for the companionship and amusement of their people.\nTheir origin dates hundreds of years before the time of Christ when the very wealthy Chinese bred them for \ncompanions and status. An elderly, long-time breeder in England told me a tale many years ago. She said the Pug \nwas so extremely pampered by the ancient Chinese that Pug puppies were often nursed by human wet nurses so the \nadored Pug bi",
