          "text": "les to get even with you for a perceived injustice that you have done to them.\nMy first Pug never failed to leave a present on my pillow each and every time I left the house without taking her. \nShe was perfectly house trained otherwise. Needless to say, she almost always left the house with me.\nWhen old-time Pug owners get together at our national specialty, it is common for us to challenge each other with \nthe worst tale of Pug behaviour. You may wonder why there was ever a second Pug in any h",
