        {
          "text": "other with \nthe worst tale of Pug behaviour. You may wonder why there was ever a second Pug in any household? We have all \nasked this question at times, but of course, we know the answer. There isn\u2019t another breed just like a Pug and when \nyou are hooked on their charm \u2013 you are hooked!\nLiving with Pugs\nPugs are suspended in life at the irresponsible age of a two year old child. \nThey must be continually and forever watched over and protected. Most of the instincts that other breeds have for \nsa",
